            <a href="/tevu-kontrole" class="font-heading font-bold text-foreground text-lg group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200 leading-tight">Tėvų kontrolė</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed">Geriausios programėlės vaikų apsaugai internete — ekrano laiko valdymas, turinio filtravimas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/tevu-kontrole" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-heading font-semibold text-primary mt-auto pt-4  hover:underline">
          Skaityti daugiau <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group relative rounded-xl border border-border/50 bg-card p-5 md:p-6 glow-border glow-border-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg h-full flex flex-col">
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-3">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-primary/8 border border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-primary-foreground transition-all duration-300 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <a href="/slaptazodziu-saugumas" class="font-heading font-bold text-foreground text-lg group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200 leading-tight">Slaptažodžių saugumas</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed">Kaip kurti stiprius slaptažodžius, naudoti tvarkykles ir apsaugoti paskyras.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/slaptazodziu-saugumas" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-heading font-semibold text-primary mt-auto pt-4  hover:underline">
          Skaityti daugiau <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group relative rounded-xl border border-border/50 bg-card p-5 md:p-6 glow-border glow-border-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg h-full flex flex-col">
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-3">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-primary/8 border border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-primary-foreground transition-all duration-300 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <a href="/virusai/kompiuterinis-virusas" class="font-heading font-bold text-foreground text-lg group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200 leading-tight">Virusai ir grėsmės</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed">Kas yra kompiuterinis virusas, kaip veikia malware ir kaip nuo jų apsisaugoti.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/virusai/kompiuterinis-virusas" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-heading font-semibold text-primary mt-auto pt-4  hover:underline">
          Skaityti daugiau <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <!-- TOP 3 -->
  <section class="border-y border-border/40 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] font-heading font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.12em] mb-3">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
          <span>2026 m. lyderiai</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">Top 3 antivirusinės programos</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm">Greitas žvilgsnis į geriausius sprendimus — detalus palyginimas laukia antivirusinių puslapyje.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        
        <div class="relative rounded-xl border bg-card p-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg border-primary/30 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[10px] font-heading font-bold text-primary-foreground bg-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow-sm">🥇 Nr. 1 pasirinkimas</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 mt-1">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-muted/60 border border-border/40 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shrink-0">
              <img src="https://dkwffdnrailtqvrxiulw.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/media/logos/norton-logo.png" alt="Norton 360" class="w-7 h-7 object-contain" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-foreground text-sm">Norton 360</h3>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5">
    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-amber-400 text-amber-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg><svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-amber-400 text-amber-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg><svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-amber-400 text-amber-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg><svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-amber-400 text-amber-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg><svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 fill-amber-400 text-amber-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
    <span class="ml-1.5 text-xs font-bold text-foreground tabular-nums">4.8</span>
  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3 leading-relaxed line-clamp-2">Visapusiška apsauga su VPN, slaptažodžių tvarkykle, debesų saugykla ir sukčių apsauga. Planai nuo 1 iki 10 įrenginių.</p>
          
          <div class="space-y-1.5 mb-4">
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <span class="text-xs text-foreground">Puikus virusų aptikimas</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
